    show bg kim_luziim_dorm
    show luziim at center_1
    with dissolve

    "It was brighter than she wanted it to be, but she couldn’t ignore that her roommate, 
    Luziim, was already fully dressed."

    ki "Oh, jeez, what time is it?"

