    ki "I try, at least."

    # [Sound: rustling of cloth or a heavy bag.]

    ki "Anyway, I’m ready. You ready to go?"

    l "Aw, hell yeah!"

    l "Seriously, a hiking and camping trip during orientation? I’ve been hyped for 
    months."

    ki "I know, right? Me too!"

